  <span id="freeText3183521701400357787" style="display:none">Coronavirus is NOT the name of the 21stC plague. The plague devastated cities, killing large chunks of their population. Coronavirus kills in extremely small percentages and among those killed, the vast majority are older and weaker people. Thus, the impact in lives between a real plague and coronavirus is vastly different.<br /><br />The measures taken against coronavirus is a small glimpse to those in a plague so in that regard, there's some foundation for parallels.</span>
